HEADWORD: Georgium Sidus
<hw>Geor"gi*um Si`dus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[NL., the star of
<ets>George</ets> (III. of England).]</ety> <fld>(Astron.)</fld>
<def>The planet Uranus, so named by its discoverer, Sir W.
